README for virtualbox-bin

PRECAUTION

    If you have any machines in a saved state it is recommeneded that
    you shut them down before updating this port.

NOTE

    If you wish for the Virtual Box drivers to be loaded on boot then
    edit /etc/rc.local config file and add something similar to this.

    if [ -f /sbin/rcvboxdrv ]; then
        rcvboxdrv start
    fi
